.SH "NAME"
ccwgroup_create_dev \- create and register a ccw group device
.SH "SYNOPSIS"
.HP \w'int\ ccwgroup_create_dev('u
.BI "int ccwgroup_create_dev(struct\ device\ *\ " "parent" ", struct\ ccwgroup_driver\ *\ " "gdrv" ", int\ " "num_devices" ", const\ char\ *\ " "buf" ");"
.SH "ARGUMENTS"
.PP
\fIparent\fR
.RS 4
parent device for the new device
.RE
.PP
\fIgdrv\fR
.RS 4
driver for the new group device
.RE
.PP
\fInum_devices\fR
.RS 4
number of slave devices
.RE
.PP
\fIbuf\fR
.RS 4
buffer containing comma separated bus ids of slave devices
.RE
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
.PP
Create and register a new ccw group device as a child of
\fIparent\fR\&. Slave devices are obtained from the list of bus ids given in
\fIbuf\fR\&.
.SH "RETURN"
.PP
\fB0\fR
on success and an error code on failure\&.
